text: Jan Stráský (24 December 1940 – 6 November 2019) was a Czech politician. He was the last Prime Minister of Czechoslovakia serving in 1992. He died on November 6, 2019 in the Czech capital at age 78. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Presidents of Czechoslovakia Category:Prime ministers of Czechoslovakia
